      window.onkeydown = (e) => {
          if (e.ctrlKey || e.altKey || e.shiftKey || e.metaKey) {
              return;
          }
          
          if (e.key == "ArrowLeft") {
              window.location.href = 'channel-buffering';
          }
          
          
          if (e.key == "ArrowRight") {
              window.location.href = 'channel-directions';
          }
          
      }
  </script>
  <body>
    <div class="example" id="channel-synchronization">
      <h2><a href="./">Go в примери</a>: Съгласуване чрез канал</h2>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Можем да ползваме канали, за да съгласуваме<sup class="footnote-ref" id="fnref:synchro"><a href="#fn:synchro">1</a></sup>
изпълнението на различни гозадачи. Тук имаме пример с
получаване на данни, което спира изпълнението на цялата
програма, изчаквайки я да приключи.<sup class="footnote-ref" id="fnref:blocking-rcv"><a href="#fn:blocking-rcv">2</a></sup>
Когато изчаквате множество гозадачи да приключат, може
да предпочетете да използвате можествено изчакване. То
е осъществено чрез структурата
<a href="waitgroups"><code>WaitGroup</code></a> в пакета <code>sync</code>.</p>

<div class="footnotes">

<hr />

<ol>
<li id="fn:synchro">synchronization – съгласуване</li>

<li id="fn:blocking-rcv">blocking receive – блокиращо получаване</li>
</ol>

</div>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            <a href="https://go.dev/play/p/blNoxHh3dGK"><img title="Run code" src="play.png" class="run" /></a><img title="Copy code" src="clipboard.png" class="copy" />
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">package</span> <span class="nx">main</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s">&#34;fmt&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s">&#34;time&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Това е функцията, която ще изпълним в гозадача. Канала
<code>готово</code> ще използваме, за да уведомим друга
гозадача (програмата ни), че тази функция е приключила.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">func</span> <span class="nx">работник</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">готово</span> <span class="kd">chan</span> <span class="kt">bool</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;работя...&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">time</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">time</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">Second</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;готово&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Изпращаме стойност като съобщение, че сме готови.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">готово</span> <span class="o">&lt;-</span> <span class="kc">true</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">func</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Пускаме гозадачата <code>работник</code> и ѝ подаваме канала,
по който да изпрати съобщението.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">готово</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="nb">make</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kd">chan</span> <span class="kt">bool</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">go</span> <span class="nx">работник</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">готово</span><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Изпълнението спира и чака, докато получи съобщение
от работника по канала.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="o">&lt;-</span><span class="nx">готово</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gp">$</span> go run channel-synchronization.go
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">работя...готово</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Ако премахнете реда с <code>&lt;- готово</code>, програмата
най-вероятно ще приключи преди <code>работник</code>а да свърши
работа и може би преди да е започнал.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      
